vision the XES extension log format to be a solid\nbased for the creation of a (semi-)automatic analysis pipeline, which can\nsupport domain experts by automatically providing data visualization, or even\nprocess insights.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Jun 2022 21:43:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-24"}
